name: berth (exp)
comment: Works as a buffer for unloading H0-DBT at the exporting habour and loading H18-DBT at the same time.

name: berth (imp)
comment: Works as a buffer for loading H0-DBT at the importing habour and unloading H18-DBT at the same time.
